  "texts": [
    "Companies with more patent citations will likely possess better technological advantages and a competitive societal market.",
    "As a result, patent citation is an indicator to evaluate a firm's invention and technological creativity in the market.",
    "Innovations: Business model innovation (BMI) (Acciarini et al. 2023) plays essential roles for firms to maintain competitive.",
    "Innovations bring new ideas or creation to the table by investors or entrepreneurs.",
    "Innovations and patents go hand in hand, as the new innovation helps the authority grant patent to investors."
  ]
}